Meravellosa gent.

1330
01:40:47,377 --> 01:40:49,937
Paloma!

1331
01:40:52,612 --> 01:40:53,921
- Mare meva quin moment.

1332
01:40:54,531 --> 01:40:59,331
{\an5}-Coloma Sant Basili, brava!

1333
