1423
01:46:46,435 --> 01:46:47,595
{\an8}(Música)

1424
01:47:02,245 --> 01:47:05,747
Benvinguts a
"Top Xef Dolços i Famosos".

1425
01:47:05,767 --> 01:47:08,176
-Comença ja la conya!
-Perfecte.

1426
